name: Kutter: Kut the Enemies (Dead)
description:
This is part of the Kutter series, in this edition you have zombies fighting against you. 

I don't think this works on ARM, but you can always try (I don't have an ARM CPU).

Warning: This project is in development. This project has been officially discontinued. 

I am not responsible for any damage with this software. This product comes with no warranty, use at your own risk.

I'm not a Microsoft or Apple verified developer :(, so you may encounter problems. Windows and Linux may also block it from running.

Windows (prevention from running, with SmartScreen): Press Advanced -> Run Anyway.
